(434, 152, '_sr_pagebuilder', '[wolf  wrapper="wrapper" parallax="true" captionparallax="true" randomhorizontaloffset="false" mouseparallax="false"][wolfitem size="wfull" speed="0.7" image="http://spab-rice.com/wordpress/demo/avoc-demo/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/600x400-light.jpg" imagelink="url" url="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/portfolio_category/ui-and-ux-design/" lightbox="" youtube="" vimeo="" captionshow="true" imageposition="wright" customcaptionwidth="55%" customimagewidth="55%" captionposition="overlay"]<h3><strong>UI & UX Design</strong></h3><p>[sr-subtitle size="h5" alignment="auto"]Interfaces and Interactions[/sr-subtitle]</p><p>If you need a web designer, hire someone else. If you want someone to help you make you money using good design, you hire me. I use qualitative and quantitative data to back up decisions, and have <em>both</em> the design and development chops to make them real.</p>[/wolfitem][wolfitem size="wfull" speed="0.7" image="http://spab-rice.com/wordpress/demo/avoc-demo/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/600x400-light.jpg" imagelink="url" url="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/portfolio_category/web-development/" lightbox="" youtube="" vimeo="" captionshow="true" imageposition="wleft" customcaptionwidth="55%" customimagewidth="55%" captionposition="overlay"]<h3><strong>Web Development</strong></h3><p>[sr-subtitle size="h5" alignment="auto"]Great sites on a budget[/sr-subtitle]</p><p>I specialise in websites with special functionalities: membership areas, protected online shops, magazines, and other specific cases. I also clean and edit sites that have large content needs for better readability.</p><p>u00a0</p>[/wolfitem][wolfitem size="wfull" speed="0.7" image="http://spab-rice.com/wordpress/demo/avoc-demo/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/600x400-light.jpg" imagelink="url" url="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/portfolio_category/consulting/" lightbox="" youtube="" vimeo="" captionshow="true" imageposition="wright" customcaptionwidth="55%" customimagewidth="55%" captionposition="overlay"]<h3><strong>Design Consulting</strong></h3><p>[sr-subtitle size="h5" alignment="auto"]Because everything is designed[/sr-subtitle]</p><p>I help you redesign your brand, bring design into your organisation, or provide design-minded business consulting to accelerate your startup. Think of me as the booster rockets: I''ll get you through the tough part, you get to the moon.</p>[/wolfitem][wolfitem size="wfull" speed="0.7" image="http://spab-rice.com/wordpress/demo/avoc-demo/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/600x400-light.jpg" imagelink="url" url="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/portfolio_category/print-design/" lightbox="" youtube="" vimeo="" captionshow="true" imageposition="wleft" customcaptionwidth="55%" customimagewidth="55%" captionposition="overlay"]<h3><strong>Print & Packaging Design</strong></h3><p>[sr-subtitle size="h5" alignment="auto"]I love beautiful boxes[/sr-subtitle]</p><p>I design packaging products, sleeves, and labeling with a focus on readability and shelf placement analysis. Also experienced in designing quality in-store menus or large-scale event graphics, booklets, and infographics.</p>[/wolfitem][/wolf][columnsection  wrapper="wrapper"][col size="one-full" last="last-col"]<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Common Projects:</strong></h2>[/col][/columnsection][spacer  size="small"][columnsection  wrapper="wrapper"][col size="one-third"]<p style="text-align: center;">[iconfont type="ion-ios-monitor-outline" size="4x" color="#aabbcc"]</p><h5 style="text-align: center;">Website Redesign Projects</h5><p style="text-align: center;">Complete website facelifts built to modern standards; fully responsive, content-formatted, user-loving websites and web apps.</p>[/col][col size="one-third"]<p style="text-align: center;">[iconfont type="ion-ionic" size="4x" color="#aabbcc"]</p><h5 style="text-align: center;">Small Business Consulting</h5><p style="text-align: center;">If you''ve got an idea, I can help you get to your first dollar. I use rapid prototyping and design sprints to develop awesome MVPs.</p>[/col][col size="one-third" last="last-col"]<p style="text-align: center;">[iconfont type="ion-ios-book-outline" size="4x" color="#aabbcc"]</p><h5 style="text-align: center;">Curriculum Development</h5><p style="text-align: center;">I design and develop framework-compliant practical classes for schools around the world so they can bring code to their classrooms.</p>[/col][/columnsection][spacer  size="big"][columnsection wrapper="wrapper-mini" animation="false"][col size="one-full" last="last-col" animation="false"]<h3 style="text-align: center;">Contact</h3><p>[contact-form-7 id="252" title="Main Contact Form"]</p>[/col][/columnsection]'),
