(621, 57, '_sr_pagebuilder', '[wolf  wrapper="wrapper" parallax="true" captionparallax="true" randomhorizontaloffset="false" mouseparallax="false"][wolfitem size="whalf" speed="" image="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Portfolio-Items-HeaderBg_Weesper-v1.jpg" imagelink="lightbox" url="" lightbox="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Portfolio-Items-HeaderBg_Weesper-v1.jpg" youtube="" vimeo="" captionshow="false" imageposition="wleft" customcaptionwidth="" customimagewidth="" captionposition="overlay"][/wolfitem][wolfitem size="whalf" speed="" image="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/weesper-new-home-ashwin.jpg" imagelink="false" url="" lightbox="" youtube="" vimeo="" captionshow="false" imageposition="wleft" customcaptionwidth="" customimagewidth="" captionposition="overlay"][/wolfitem][wolfitem size="whalf" speed="" image="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/weesper-new-dash-ashwin-v2.jpg" imagelink="false" url="" lightbox="" youtube="" vimeo="" captionshow="false" imageposition="wleft" customcaptionwidth="" customimagewidth="" captionposition="overlay"][/wolfitem][wolfitem size="whalf" speed="" image="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Portfolio-Items-Weesper-v4.png" imagelink="false" url="" lightbox="" youtube="" vimeo="" captionshow="false" imageposition="wleft" customcaptionwidth="" customimagewidth="" captionposition="overlay"][/wolfitem][wolfitem size="whalf" speed="" image="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Portfolio-Items-Weesper-v3.png" imagelink="false" url="" lightbox="" youtube="" vimeo="" captionshow="false" imageposition="wleft" customcaptionwidth="" customimagewidth="" captionposition="overlay"][/wolfitem][wolfitem size="whalf" speed="" image="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/weesper-chatbot-ux-flow.jpg" imagelink="lightbox" url="" lightbox="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/weesper-chatbot-ux-flow.jpg" youtube="" vimeo="" captionshow="false" imageposition="wleft" customcaptionwidth="" customimagewidth="" captionposition="overlay"][/wolfitem][/wolf][columnsection  wrapper="wrapper"][col size="one-full" last="last-col"]<h4 style="text-align: center;"><strong>User Interface & User Experience</strong></h4><p>[sr-subtitle size="h5" alignment="center"]Highlights[/sr-subtitle]</p>[/col][/columnsection][spacer  size="small"][columnsection  wrapper="wrapper-mini" animation="false"][col size="one-full" last="last-col" animation="false"]<h5 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Live Link:</strong> <a style="color: #1bafdf;" href="http://weesper.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://weesper.com</a></h5><ul><li>Custom-developed (scripted) cutesy <strong>chatbot</strong> to increase sign-up conversions</li><li>Choose-Your-Own-Price slider with <strong>colour indicators</strong> built in Bootstrap</li><li>Admin Dashboard uses just two <strong>direct-action</strong> menu items</li><li>Referrals are done using a <strong>chunking process</strong> to capture insight without fatiguing users</li></ul>[/col][/columnsection][spacer  size="small"][columnsection  wrapper="wrapper" animation="false"][col size="one-third" animation="false"]<p>[sr-subtitle size="h5" alignment="center"]Design[/sr-subtitle]</p><p>Completed in Illustrator with over 50 iterations per version (v0, v1, v1.1), this project has a dedicate Homepage for Referrers and Clients, a Dashboard for each user type, and a number of condensed forms.</p>[/col][col size="one-third" animation="false"]<p>[sr-subtitle size="h5" alignment="center"]Business[/sr-subtitle]</p><p>I''ve been working with Weesper since January 2017 to build the platform through the early stages. I''ve consulted on increasing conversions, improving performance, marketing strategy and copywriting.</p>[/col][col size="one-third" last="last-col" animation="false"]<p>[sr-subtitle size="h5" alignment="center"]Technology[/sr-subtitle]</p><p>Designed for responsive behaviour but with specialised improvements for every platform. For example, the chatbot works flawlessly on mobile and forms feature bigger thumb-friendly sizes. CSS consults included.</p>[/col][/columnsection][spacer  size="small"]'),
