(55, 1, '2014-01-01 14:28:17', '2014-01-01 14:28:17', '[wolf wrapper="wrapper" parallax="true" captionparallax="true" randomhorizontaloffset="false" mouseparallax="false"][wolfitem size="wfull" speed="1.4" image="http://spab-rice.com/wordpress/demo/avoc-demo/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/600x400-light.jpg" imagelink="false" url="" lightbox="" youtube="" vimeo="" captionshow="true" imageposition="wright" customcaptionwidth="60%" customimagewidth="" captionposition="overlay"]\r\n\r\n[sr-subtitle size="h5" alignment="auto"]App Prototype[/sr-subtitle]\r\n<h1><strong>Marco</strong></h1>\r\n[/wolfitem][/wolf][columnsection wrapper="wrapper-mini"][col size="one-full" last="last-col"]\r\n<h6><strong>Idea</strong></h6>\r\nEfimer is a project based on the concept that fashion is ephemeral. To represent this idea I designed a haute couture collection made by vegetables, which are ephemeral too. I decided to paint the vegetables to give uniformity at the clothes and express the purity that provides the white color.\r\n<h6><strong>Technologies</strong></h6>\r\nAxure - Prototyping\r\nHTML5/CSS3 - Front-End\r\njQuery Mobile - Front-End\r\n<h6><strong>Art Direction</strong></h6>\r\nAshwin Anandani\r\n\r\n[/col][/columnsection][spacer size="big"][columnsection wrapper="wrapper"][col size="one-full" last="last-col"][sr-gallery images="image~~10~~http://spab-rice.com/wordpress/demo/avoc-demo/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/600x400-light-150x150.jpg|||image~~10~~http://spab-rice.com/wordpress/demo/avoc-demo/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/600x400-light-150x150.jpg" type="gallery" columns="2" animation="delayed" tilesize="300" spaced="yes" lightbox="no"][sr-gallery images="image~~14~~http://www.spab-rice.com/wordpress/demo/avoc-demo/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/1100x600-light-150x150.jpg" type="gallery" columns="1" animation="delayed" tilesize="300" spaced="yes" lightbox="no"][sr-gallery images="image~~10~~http://www.spab-rice.com/wordpress/demo/avoc-demo/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/600x400-light-150x150.jpg|||image~~10~~http://www.spab-rice.com/wordpress/demo/avoc-demo/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/600x400-light-150x150.jpg" type="gallery" columns="2" animation="delayed" tilesize="300" spaced="yes" lightbox="no"][/col][/columnsection]', 'Marco', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'marco-app', '', '', '2018-03-18 17:20:22', '2018-03-18 17:20:22', '', 0, 'http://www.spab-rice.com/wordpress/demo/avoc-demo/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=55', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0),
