om/portfoliov2/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/weesper-chatbot-ux-flow.jpg" youtube="" vimeo="" captionshow="false" imageposition="wleft" customcaptionwidth="" customimagewidth="" captionposition="overlay"][/wolfitem][/wolf][columnsection wrapper="wrapper"][col size="one-full" last="last-col"]\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;"><strong>User Interface &amp; User Experience</strong></h4>\r\n[sr-subtitle size="h5" alignment="center"]Highlights[/sr-subtitle]\r\n\r\n[/col][/columnsection][spacer size="small"][columnsection wrapper="wrapper-mini" animation="false"][col size="one-full" last="last-col" animation="false"]\r\n<h5 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Live Link:</strong> <a style="color: #1bafdf;" href="http://weesper.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://weesper.com</a></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Custom-developed (scripted) cutesy <strong>chatbot</strong> to increase sign-up conversions</li>\r\n 	<li>Choose-Your-Own-Price slider with <strong>colour indicators</strong> built in Bootstrap</li>\r\n 	<li>Admin Dashboard uses just two <strong>direct-action</strong> menu items</li>\r\n 	<li>Referrals are done using a <strong>chunking process</strong> to capture insight without fatiguing users</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/col][/columnsection][spacer size="small"][columnsection wrapper="wrapper" animation="false"][col size="one-third" animation="false"]\r\n\r\n[sr-subtitle size="h5" alignment="center"]Design[/sr-subtitle]\r\n\r\nCompleted in Illustrator with over 50 iterations per version (v0, v1, v1.1), this project has a dedicate Homepage for Referrers and Clients, a Dashboard for each user type, and a number of condensed forms.\r\n\r\n[/col][col size="one-third" animation="false"]\r\n\r\n[sr-subtitle size="h5" alignment="center"]Business[/sr-subtitle]\r\n\r\nI''ve been working with Weesper since January 2017 to build the platform through the early stages. I''ve consulted on increasing conversions, improving performance, marketing strategy and copywriting.\r\n\r\n[/col][col size="one-third" last="last-col" animation="false"]\r\n\r\n[sr-subtitle size="h5" alignment="center"]Technology[/sr-subtitle]\r\n\r\nDesigned for responsive behaviour but with specialised improvements for every platform. For example, the chatbot works flawlessly on mobile and forms feature bigger thumb-friendly sizes. CSS consults included.\r\n\r\n[/col][/columnsection][spacer size="small"]', 'Weesper', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'weesper-talent-referral-platform', '', '', '2018-03-18 17:19:06', '2018-03-18 17:19:06', '', 0, 'http://www.spab-rice.com/wordpress/demo/avoc-demo/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=57', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0),
