(242, 1, '2018-03-15 17:01:36', '2018-03-15 17:01:36', '[wolf wrapper="wrapper" parallax="true" captionparallax="true" randomhorizontaloffset="false" mouseparallax="false"][wolfitem size="wfull" speed="1.4" image="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/usg-talk-2.jpg" imagelink="false" url="" lightbox="" youtube="" vimeo="" captionshow="true" imageposition="wleft" customcaptionwidth="60%" customimagewidth="55%" captionposition="overlay"]\r\n<h2><span style="color: #9178ac;"><strong>Ashwin Anandani</strong></span></h2>\r\n[sr-subtitle size="h2" alignment="auto"]Minimalist design, modern technology, and good business.[/sr-subtitle]\r\n\r\n[/wolfitem][/wolf][columnsection wrapper="wrapper-small" animation="false"][col size="one-half" animation="false"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: right;"><strong>Do <span style="color: #f46f49;">more</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;">I''ve enjoyed many clients over the last 8 years leading the design of human-centred web products in fast-paced environments with limited resources.</p>\r\n[/col][col size="one-half" last="last-col" animation="false"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;"><strong>With <span style="color: #674172;">less</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Technology should enable people, so I''m not a fan of big budgets or complex setups. I encourage learning by doing, and I do so by learning.</p>\r\n[/col][/columnsection][spacer size="big"][columnsection wrapper="wrapper" animation="false"][col size="one-full" last="last-col" animation="false"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">Prefer to see a face?</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Watch me pitch my failed Kickstarter project:</em></p>\r\n[/col][/columnsection][spacer size="small"][columnsection wrapper="wrapper-small"][col size="one-full" last="last-col"]\r\n\r\n[sr-video type=inline image="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/kaleido-teaser.gif" video="youtube" id="C7hUkuqdlGw" text="Play Video"]\r\n\r\n[/col][/columnsection][spacer size="big"]', 'Experience :: Design, Business, and Technology', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '128-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-15 17:01:36', '2018-03-15 17:01:36', '', 128, 'http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/2018/03/15/128-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(247, 1, '2018-03-15 17:28:59', '2018-03-15 17:28:59', '[wolf wrapper="wrapper" parallax="true" captionparallax="true" randomhorizontaloffset="false" mouseparallax="false"][wolfitem size="wfull" speed="0.7" image="http://spab-rice.com/wordpress/demo/avoc-demo/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/600x400-light.jpg" imagelink="url" url="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/portfolio_category/ui-and-ux-design/" lightbox="" youtube="" vimeo="" captionshow="true" imageposition="wright" customcaptionwidth="55%" customimagewidth="55%" captionposition="overlay"]\r\n<h3><strong>UI &amp; UX Design</strong></h3>\r\n[sr-subtitle size="h5" alignment="auto"]Interfaces and Interactions[/sr-subtitle]\r\n\r\nIf you need a web designer, hire someone else. If you want someone to help you make you money using good design, you hire me. I use qualitative and quantitative data to back up decisions, and have <em>both</em> the design and development chops to make them real.\r\n\r\n[/wolfitem][wolfitem size="wfull" speed="0.7" image="http://spab-rice.com/wordpress/demo/avoc-demo/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/600x400-light.jpg" imagelink="url" url="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/portfolio_category/web-development/" lightbox="" youtube="" vimeo="" captionshow="true" imageposition="wleft" customcaptionwidth="55%" customimagewidth="55%" captionposition="overlay"]\r\n<h3><strong>Web Development</strong></h3>\r\n[sr-subtitle size="h5" alignment="auto"]Great sites on a budget[/sr-subtitle]\r\n\r\nI specialise in websites with special functionalities: membership areas, protected online shops, magazines, and other specific cases. I also clean and edit sites that have large content needs for better readability.\r\n\r\nu00a0\r\n\r\n[/wolfitem][wolfitem size="wfull" speed="0.7" image="http://spab-rice.com/wordpress/demo/avoc-demo/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/600x400-light.jpg" imagelink="url" url="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/portfolio_category/consulting/" lightbox="" youtube="" vimeo="" captionshow="true" imageposition="wright" customcaptionwidth="55%" customimagewidth="55%" captionposition="overlay"]\r\n<h3><strong>Design Consulting</strong></h3>\r\n[sr-subtitle size="h5" alignment="auto"]Because everything is designed[/sr-subtitle]\r\n\r\nI help you redesign your brand, bring design into your organisation, or provide design-minded business consulting to accelerate your startup. Think of me as the booster rockets: I''ll get you through the tough part, you get to the moon.\r\n\r\n[/wolfitem][wolfitem size="wfull" speed="0.7" image="http://spab-rice.com/wordpress/demo/avoc-demo/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/600x400-light.jpg" imagelink="url" url="http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/portfolio_category/print-design/" lightbox="" youtube="" vimeo="" captionshow="true" imageposition="wright" customcaptionwidth="55%" customimagewidth="55%" captionposition="overlay"]\r\n<h3><strong>Print &amp; Packaging Design</strong></h3>\r\n[sr-subtitle size="h5" alignment="auto"]I love beautiful boxes[/sr-subtitle]\r\n\r\nI design packaging products, sleeves, and labeling with a focus on readability and shelf placement analysis. Also experienced in designing quality in-store menus or large-scale event graphics, booklets, and infographics.\r\n\r\n[/wolfitem][/wolf][columnsection wrapper="wrapper"][col size="one-full" last="last-col"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Common Projects:</strong></h2>\r\n[/col][/columnsection][spacer size="small"][columnsection wrapper="wrapper"][col size="one-third"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">[iconfont type="ion-ios-monitor-outline" size="4x" color="#4b425e"]</p>\r\n\r\n<h5 style="text-align: center;">Website Redesign Projects</h5>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Complete website facelifts built to modern standards; fully responsive, content-formatted, user-loving websites and web apps.</p>\r\n[/col][col size="one-third"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">[iconfont type="ion-ionic" size="4x" color="#4b425e"]</p>\r\n\r\n<h5 style="text-align: center;">Small Business Consulting</h5>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">If you''ve got an idea, I can help you get to your first dollar. I use rapid prototyping and design sprints to develop awesome MVPs.</p>\r\n[/col][col size="one-third" last="last-col"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">[iconfont type="ion-ios-book-outline" size="4x" color="#4b425e"]</p>\r\n\r\n<h5 style="text-align: center;">Curriculum Development</h5>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">I design and develop framework-compliant practical classes for schools around the world so they can bring code to their classrooms.</p>\r\n[/col][/columnsection][spacer size="big"]', 'What I Do', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '152-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-15 17:28:59', '2018-03-15 17:28:59', '', 152, 'http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/2018/03/15/152-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
