ong> built in Bootstrap</li>\r\n 	<li>Admin Dashboard uses just two <strong>direct-action</strong> menu items</li>\r\n 	<li>Referrals are done using a <strong>chunking process</strong> to capture insight without fatiguing users</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/col][col size="one-half" last="last-col"]\r\n\r\n<strong>Live Link:</strong> <a href="http://weesper.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://weesper.com</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Design:</strong> Completed in Illustrator with over 50 iterations per version, this project has a dedicate Homepage for Referrers and Clients, a Dashboard for each user type, and a number of condensed forms.\r\n\r\n<strong>Business:</strong> I''ve been working with Weesper since January 2017 to build the platform through its various stages (MVP, v0, v1, and now v1.1). Over this time, I''ve provided advice on increasing conversions, improving performance, marketing strategy, and even written a lot of the copy.\r\n\r\n<strong>Technology:</strong> Designed for responsive behaviour but with specialised improvements for every platform. For example, the chatbot works flawlessly on mobile and forms feature bigger thumb-friendly sizes. In most cases, I also provided the relevant CSS.\r\n\r\n[/col][/columnsection]', 'Weesper', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '57-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-16 16:54:22', '2018-03-16 16:54:22', '', 57, 'http://carryuto.com/portfoliov2/2018/03/16/57-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
